<section sectnbr = "4A">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AFRAP70A4106021" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Vérification de fonctionnement du servofrein 
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Avant d&#39;effectuer la vérification, s&#39;assurer qu&#39;il n&#39;y a pas d&#39;air dans la canalisation hydraulique. 
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servinfosub id = "AFRAP70A4106021001">
<title>
Vérification de l&#39;hermétisme 
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Faire démarrer le moteur. 
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Faire tourner le moteur pendant 1 à 2 minutes, puis l&#39;arrêter. 
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Enfoncer la pédale de frein plusieurs fois avec la même force que pour un freinage normal afin d&#39;observer les changements de la course de pédale. Le servofrein est étanche à l&#39;air si la course de pédale se réduit chaque fois que la pédale est enfoncée. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.619mm" ver = "01" gw = "131" gh = "126"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.501in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.579in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.631in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1ère 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
2ème 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
3ème 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Si la course de pédale ne change pas, l&#39;étanchéité à l&#39;air du servofrein est défectueuse. 
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
En cas de problème, vérifier les canalisations à dépression ainsi que les pièces assurant l&#39;étanchéité et remplacer toute pièce défectueuse. Ensuite, répéter la totalité du test. 
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.196mm" ver = "01" gw = "132" gh = "125"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.030in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1ère, 2ème, 3ème 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AFRAP70A4106021002">
<title>
Vérification du fonctionnement 
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Moteur coupé, enfoncer la pédale de frein à plusieurs reprises avec la même force et s&#39;assurer que la course de pédale ne change pas. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.323mm" ver = "01" gw = "162" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Faire démarrer le moteur tout en enfonçant la pédale de frein. Si la course de pédale augmente un peu, le fonctionnement du servofrein est correct. Si la course de pédale ne change pas, cela indique un dysfonctionnement du servofrein. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410008.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.958mm" ver = "01" gw = "173" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AFRAP70A4106021003">
<title>
Vérification de l&#39;hermétisme en charge 
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Faire tourner le moteur et enfoncer la pédale de frein. Arrêter ensuite le moteur tout en maintenant la pédale de frein enfoncée. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.805mm" ver = "01" gw = "123" gh = "130"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.232in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.628in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Maintenir enfoncée 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Maintenir la pédale de frein enfoncée pendant 30 secondes. Si la hauteur de pédale reste inchangée, le servofrein fonctionne correctement. Si la hauteur de pédale change, le servofrein ne fonctionne pas correctement. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.059mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "131"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.643in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.800in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Maintenir enfoncée 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
T: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
30 secondes
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
